her include them or remove the dependency array.",["519"],"'deletedProd' is assigned a value but never used.",["520"],"'setUsers' is defined but never used.","'allowedExtensions' is assigned a value but never used.",["521"],"'useEffect' is defined but never used.","'isAction' is defined but never used.",["522"],"Assignments to the 'id' variable from inside React Hook useEffect will be lost after each render. To preserve the value over time, store it in a useRef Hook and keep the mutable value in the '.current' property. Otherwise, you can move this variable directly inside useEffect.","MemberExpression","'type' is defined but never used.","'putOnDB' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useMemo has a missing dependency: 'users'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["523"],"'result' is assigned a value but never used.",["524"],"The 'friendMessages' logical expression could make the dependencies of useEffect Hook (at line 55) change on every render. To fix this, wrap the initialization of 'friendMessages' in its own useMemo() Hook.","Expected '!==' and instead saw '!='.",{"desc":"525","fix":"526"},{"desc":"527","fix":"528"},{"desc":"529","fix":"530"},{"desc":"531","fix":"532"},{"desc":"531","fix":"533"},[2613,2613]," rel=\"noreferrer\"",{"desc":"531","fix":"534"},{"desc":"535","fix":"536"},{"desc":"537","fix":"538"},{"desc":"539","fix":"540"},{"desc":"531","fix":"541"},{"desc":"531","fix":"542"},{"desc":"543","fix":"544"},{"desc":"545","fix":"546"},{"desc":"537","fix":"547"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [dispatch, navigate]",{"range":"548","text":"549"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [photo, showLikedUsers]",{"range":"550","text":"551"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [logedUser?.friends, users]",{"range":"552","text":"553"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [dispatch]",{"range":"554","text":"555"},{"range":"556","text":"555"},{"range":"557","text":"555"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [filteredProducts, searc